---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import MeHomeOffice from '../../assets/images/me-home-office.jpg'
---

<Layout title="about | timuism | the online home of timothy long">
	<article class="font-medium">
		<h2 class="text-2xl">About</h2>

    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-rows-1 md:grid-rows-1 md:grid-cols-1 gap-6 items-stretch">
      <figure>
        <img 
          src={MeHomeOffice} 
          alt="Photo of Tim at his home office"  
          class="h-full border-4 border-white/5 rounded" 
        />
      </figure>
    </div>

    <p class="longform-p mt-12">
      I'm a user interface developer that loves building web apps. I'm always striving to create innovative and creative designs that will bring user experience to the next level. I'm passionate about creating unique applications that are both visually stimulating and functional.
    </p>

    <h4 class="">Looking to hire me?</h4>
    <p class="longform-p mt-12">
      At this time, I am not actively looking for work. If you would like to hire me as a consultant for anything web related, feel free to <a href="mailto:tim@timuism.com" class="text-primary underline hover:text-secondary duration-200">contact me</a>! If you are looking for my resume, feel free to reach out as well. I'd encourage you to <a href="https://linkedin.com/timuism" target="_blank" class="text-primary underline hover:text-secondary duration-200">connect with me on LinkedIn</a>.
    </p>

    <p class="longform-p mt-12">
      Outside of work, I'm rarely bored. I enjoy cooking, video games, reading and spending time with my daughter and girlfriend. I'm a self-taught musician and play gigs and write music. I love gardening and am interest in growing most of my own food. 
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

